{"tid":1653953,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國傳冀簽首階段貿易協議前進行更多談判","createTime":"2019-10-14T10:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T01:00:31.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"77bb84ca7d9b335730fc4bd560cc582564417a18","tid":1653953,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"又傾過....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n17:58 【中國傳冀簽首階段貿易協議前進行更多談判】外電引述知情人士透露，中國希望最快在10月底進行進一步談判，以確定被美國總統特朗普稱為「第一階段」貿易協議的細節，以待國家主席習近平同意簽署。<br />\n<br />\n其中一位人士稱，北京可能派出由國務院副總理劉鶴率領的...<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=310fb31d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a>"},{"pid":"3df139346651e40bb44359608d7677b62fc2ba52","tid":1653953,"uid":33907,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"真係想傾到完 睇嚟今晚發嬲加夠40%"},{"pid":"a94f89bac998bb86e6a499e264fc67cdd3fbdd80","tid":1653953,"uid":12447,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:31:19.000Z","msg":"傾左年幾<br />\n仲傾乜春<br />\n反枱啦"},{"pid":"9a9b6a9a7e63623bf90288dc6faad87b434d9067","tid":1653953,"uid":186543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:38:13.000Z","msg":"爆drop"},{"pid":"53d49f167c9084a5fb3deae5c44b40528f35dee3","tid":1653953,"uid":44454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"其實劉鶴 飛來飛去 會唔會好煩呀， 不如長駐美國啦"},{"pid":"86e07943079695263f1d91936e7a1e1066c120d3","tid":1653953,"uid":48139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53d49f167c9084a5fb3deae5c44b40528f35dee3","tid":1653953,"uid":44454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"其實劉鶴 飛來飛去 會唔會好煩呀， 不如長駐美國啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"佢不知幾想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0955399e38fbe848f5bd98689155047688ae06f","tid":1653953,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"887e240d844e809033b60239b5c16aff99915265","tid":1653953,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"等陣Trump爺發嬲即刻加稅,直接搶"},{"pid":"4335644a9f84db4e4a631ee101bb45b7518f3aac","tid":1653953,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"500億美元買農產品 只係換5% （2500的5%=125億）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a06db8717f56aaf23229fe2a60a5081caf23c4","tid":1653953,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":